{
  "about": "The minimum conversational phrase deck: short MSA sentences that, memorised, carry a basic conversation. Chosen so every question has its answer pattern, plus the repair phrases that keep a learner IN a conversation. Keys ph-<group>:<i> are append-only — never reorder or delete members, SRS points at indices.",
